I"<h4 id="class-exercise-short-animation">Class Exercise: Short Animation</h4>
<p>Create a video that is Halloween or voting themed and uses at least one After Effects effect. You can use type, shapes, images, and videos or some combination of the four (basically anything you want). The video should have audio and be around 10 seconds long.</p>

<p>At the end of class we will screen the videos and the top two videos in each category will win a prize. There will be a People’s Choice award and a Teacher’s Choice award.</p>

<h5 id="technical-requirements">Technical Requirements</h5>
<ul>
  <li>1920x1080</li>
  <li>Around 10 seconds long</li>
  <li>Uses at least one After Effects effect</li>
  <li>Has audio</li>
</ul>

